<p>This give me every monday date in date range. </p>  <p><strong>Question: How to get every monday and friday of week?</strong></p>  <pre><code>$start_date = date('Y-m-d'); $end_date = date('Y-m-d', strtotime($start_date . ' + 1 MONTH'));  for(     $i = strtotime('Monday', strtotime($start_date));      $i &lt;= strtotime($end_date);      $i = strtotime('+1 WEEK', $i) ) {     echo date('Y-m-d', $i). '&lt;br&gt;'; } </code></pre>  <p><strong>My Update:</strong></p>  <pre><code>$my_dates = []; for(     $i = strtotime($start_date);      $i &lt;= strtotime($end_date);      $i = strtotime('+1 DAY', $i) ) {     if(in_array(date('N', $i), array(1, 5))) {         $my_dates[] = date('Y-m-d', $i);     } }  var_dump($my_dates); </code></pre>